original_title: GCW: Devil In A New Dress
overview: On April 10 GCW presents Devil in a New Dress live on FITE straight from The Midway in San Francisco, CA. The first four matches in the lineup are announced and here they are:  Minoru Suzuki vs Mike Bailey  Biff Busick vs Masha Slamovich  Bandido vs Nick Wayne  Dark Sheik vs Joey Janela
title: GCW: Devil In A New Dress
